sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler as SubscriptionItemUpdateScheduler
    participant Repo as SubscriptionItemsRepository
    participant Prov as ProvisioningService
    participant SSH as SshExecutorService
    participant Host as Provisioned host

    Note over Scheduler: Every SUBSCRIPTION_UPDATE_SCHEDULER_INTERVAL (default 24h)
    Scheduler->>Repo: findProvisionedWithSshKey()
    Repo-->>Scheduler: items (active, with SSH key)

    loop For each item
        Scheduler->>Prov: getServerInfo(provider, providerReference)
        Prov-->>Scheduler: publicIp

        Scheduler->>Scheduler: buildAgentControllerUpdateCommand() or buildAgentManagerUpdateCommand()
        Note right of Scheduler: Command logs to /var/log/*-update.log on host

        Scheduler->>SSH: exec(host, 22, root, privateKey, command)
        SSH->>Host: SSH connect + exec
        Host->>Host: cd /opt/agent-* && docker compose up -d --pull=always
        Host-->>SSH: stdout/stderr, exit code
        SSH-->>Scheduler: result

        alt Exit code !== 0
            Scheduler->>Scheduler: log error (stderr)
        else Success
            Scheduler->>Scheduler: log "Update completed"
        end
    end
